ự - 早秋京口旅泊贈張侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Gia-H%E1%BB%B1u/author-6zYzZx8bQhzm8Wdeftq7Wg">Lý Gia Hựu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-zYImYpb82xchstT0tz3scQ">Thướng Vi tả tướng nhị thập vận - 上韋左相二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Ti%E1%BB%85n-tr%C3%AD-s%E1%BB%B1-kinh-do%C3%A3n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Tr%E1%BB%A9/poem-NrIIAlUplVGXQz8y0KLfkA">Tiễn trí sự kinh doãn Nguyễn Công Trứ - 餞致事京尹阮公著</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BA%BF-v%C4%83n/poem-eH6-j7g098C-j3cSVlJ0sg">Tự tế văn - 自祭文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
